675a5bcaf13de2be6d0e570721e99ec95e5c4de76d4ae952bdc575f7bd57dba4e3596cdeb2a2c0e2aa7af0286da01bc336cf28bbf245671edac5372331be4ecb  no-telemetry.patch
"
